reviews.reviewText: Holes were partially punched and when I contacted seller I was told I can punch/cut them out myself. I said thanks but I'd rather not eat any silicone bits I may miss that'll fall off. Tried the solid one... flies all over the air fryer unless you use objects to weight down all 4 corners. Pass on this one folks. Stick with foil and parchment. I was trying to go green but it just made me frustrated.
